{"tid":1348010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊推到各大航空停飛香港","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:01:02.000Z","uid":258327,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46d60d03b2faa0500cd913917431d9cb44c0bee7","tid":1348010,"uid":258327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"小弟最近留意到歐洲有兩間航空,BA Lufthansa,由於保安原因停飛埃及開羅<br />\n(歐美多國因為當地政局動盪及潛在恐襲危機早前已經發出旅遊警示)<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/07/20/world/british-airlines-lufthansa-cancel-flights-to-cairo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F20%2Fworld%2Fbritish-airlines-lufthansa-cancel-flights-to-cairo%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c4a75d92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F20%2Fworld%2Fbritish-airlines-lufthansa-cancel-flights-to-cairo%2F&h=f532df17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/07/20/world/british-airlines-lufthansa-cancel-flights-to-cairo/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知香港21/7咁樣嘅亂局算唔算有恐襲/安全威脅之類呢??<br />\n今日有巴打po美國United Airlines 已經宣布暫時停止航員香港過夜,<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1347311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1347311/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知有無用,就儘管試一下可唔可以上航空公司嘅<br />\nsocial media DM進行查詢<br />\n<br />\nBA<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/british_airways\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbritish_airways&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=9c2423d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/british_airways</a><br />\nANA<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/flyana_official\\\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fflyana_official%5C&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=75b4705b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/flyana_official\\</a><br />\nJAL<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jal_official_jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjal_official_jp&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=643613fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jal_official_jp</a><br />\nDelta<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/delta\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdelta&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=758cc416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/delta</a><br />\nQantas<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/qantas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fqantas&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=1f4b0a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/qantas</a><br />\nAmerica Airlines<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/americanair\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famericanair&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=f358441b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/americanair</a><br />\nAir France<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/airfrance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fairfrance&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=f453c63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/airfrance</a><br />\nLufthansa<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lufthansa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flufthansa&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=4c69ec7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lufthansa</a><br />\n華航<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chinaairlinesen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchinaairlinesen&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=2c1af023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chinaairlinesen</a><br />\n長榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/evaairus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht